results.occurrenceRemarks: These birds were very common among the lily pads that grew in the shallows of Lake Skadar. They usually didn't let the boat get very close, but this one was not concentrating on us, so we managed to approach a bit closer. This species is quite far ranging, being found all the way down to southern africa, where we saw them last summer.
